metadata.name: Squiggles #1722
metadata.description: Squiggles are a set of 10,000 non-fungible tokens (NFTs) comprised of hundreds of unique visual features and character bases. The collection is currently publicly shown to contain but is not limited to: humans, apes, flame heads, clouds, clocks, beakers, and skulls. Hundreds of unique features, costumes, and colors of the artist's palette are also included in the Squiggles collection.
